Class Strings

java.lang.Object
app.tracktune.utils.Strings
public class Strings extends Object
Centralized container for constant string literals used throughout the application.

This class provides a single place to manage UI messages, error messages, labels, and other fixed texts, facilitating easier localization and maintenance.

All fields are public static final constants representing messages or labels displayed in the UI or used internally for validation, error reporting, and status updates.
